<paragraph blockId="29.[189,1398,1608,1715]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
According to 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure" box="[350,582,1654,1681]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" pagination="83 - 142" refId="ref21502" refString="Moure J. S., Melo G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo F. 2007. Centridini Cockerell &amp; Cockerell. In: Moure J. S., Urban D. &amp; Melo G. A. R. (orgs) Catalogue of Bees (Hymenoptera, Apoidea) in the Neotropical Region: 83 - 142. Sociedade Brasileira de Entomologia, Curitibrazil." type="book chapter" year="2007">
